summary: Increases the push force of the Unrelenting Force shout
descriptionHtml:
Increases the power of the Unrelenting Force shout a lot, so that you can throw enemies high in the air with a single Fus !

v2.0

- OP Draugr Deathlords issue fixed :
  Fus throws enemies in the air but deals almost no damage,
  Ro pushes further than Fus and causes more damage,
  Dah changed back to the base version (less push than Fus and Ro, but more damage)

Special thanks to GMSTGames for reviewing my mod !
author: Biomod1155
